plot: Peggy surprises her husband Micah with a trip to Vegas, and rather than bringing her gal-pal Alexis, she makes it a couples-only trip with Tamra and Eddie. Back in Coto de Caza, Gretchen and Slade have a heart-to-heart about how his child support issues and debts are causing problems in their relationship. Meanwhile, it's the day of the Alexis Couture Fashion Preview and Vicki is a no-show.—Anonymous
